## Third-Party Software

SecureOS is based on Ubuntu 24.04 LTS and includes various open source
components, each subject to their own licenses:

- Ubuntu: Copyright Canonical Ltd. (Various licenses)
- Linux Kernel: GPL v2
- AppArmor: GPL v2
- XFCE Desktop: GPL v2 and LGPL v2
- All other included packages retain their original licenses

For specific license information about included packages, please refer to
/usr/share/doc/[package-name]/copyright on an installed system.
